  "prompt": "What does \u201csocially inept\u201d mean?",
  "response": "\"Socially inept\" refers to a lack of social skills or difficulty in navigating social situations. A person who is socially inept might struggle with understanding social cues, maintaining conversations, or building relationships. They may find it challenging to interact smoothly with others or follow the unwritten rules of social behavior. This term does not necessarily imply any negative traits about a person's character; it simply describes difficulties in social engagement.",
